** [[Sz<U+00E9>kely Land]]
** [[<U+021A>ara Mo<U+021B>ilor]]
** [[<U+021A>ara N<U+0103>s<U+0103>udului]] (N<U+00F6>snerland/Nasz<U+00F3>d vid<U+00E9>ke)
